WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.000
<v Sebastian>Thanks for making the time. Walk me through how AI tools got rolled out at your company.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.000
<v P1>Sure. Our CTO pushed for Copilot about a year ago, and ChatGPT Enterprise followed.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:18.000
<v P1>Honestly the rollout was chaotic, nobody measured anything.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:24.000
<v Sebastian>The last time someone senior asked whether the AI investment is working, what happened?

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:34.000
<v P1>Our CFO asked exactly that in March. We had nothing. I built a spreadsheet from the Copilot dashboard, it took me a week and told us almost nothing about quality.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
<v Sebastian>Who would own the budget if you bought something to fix that?

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:48.000
<v P1>That would be my budget, VP Engineering. I'd want a pilot with one team first, and yes, we'd pay for a pilot if the data looks real.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:55.000
<v Sebastian>If this needs each engineer to run the analysis themselves, what fraction would actually do it?

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:04.000
<v P1>Maybe two thirds if we make it part of onboarding. At that coverage a dashboard would still be useful for the enablement decisions I mentioned.
